split
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:[dog trials] 1. a departure of one of three competition sheep from the others during a trial run. 2. a successful division of a group of six competition sheep into two trios by a dog competitor.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
